歲 <br />\n<br />\n如果30歲一貧如洗就係失敗, 起碼應該要有番2年積蓄/打工經驗係身的話, 即係28歲就係極限<br />\n<br />\n換句話講, 23歲一出身就要放膽試, 問題在於呢個歲數多數無錢無身, 仲狽住一身學費債, 儲得舊本金黎可以搵啲野搞下, 分分鐘已經26,7 <br />\n<br />\n........屌!! 即係講緊我自己"},{"pid":"8af655ee981622f0726cfebf2263873554056e04","tid":293172,"uid":35621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想做乜就試<br />\n<br />\n行年廿二 月入20-23k( pt + ft 6日工)<br />\n上一年拎左廿萬去外國讀19 foundation<br />\n而家yr 1</blockquote><br />\n廿二搵23K好勁喎巴打<br />\n仲有20萬<br />\n<br />\n廿二大把人仲讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe4b3dac4b9fee5770a91a981525f3799779117","tid":293172,"uid":71175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明白樓主感受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 27 歲搵24k 有女 有1M 儲蓄 <br />\n          都係一事無成 準備辭職搵第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n24k有 1m儲蓄咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e062ffeacfdd26c8ccef1ad2f9a54c7d2c3c5e","tid":293172,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好明白樓主感受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 27 歲搵24k 有女 有1M 儲蓄 <br />\n          都係一事無成 準備辭職搵第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n24k有 1m儲蓄咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434290d530ca850fa2f8e31f5421582a2130f781","tid":293172,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>悶得滯想唔要飯碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頂, 的確係你講咁樣<br />\n<br />\n明明應該心足, 慢慢腳踏實地咁儲錢, 慢慢成家立室<br />\n<br />\n但係個心好似有蟻咬咁, 覺得身邊朋友個個都彈起, 自己仲係咁樣唔得</blockquote